title: Ryan Reynolds, Michael Bublé among celebs tweeting #Plankthecurve videos to help fight COVID-19
description: Canadian celebrities including Deadpool actor Ryan Reynolds and Superbad's Seth Rogen are asking people to stay home and prevent the spread of COVID-19 after Prime Minister Justin Trudeau asked for help to get the message across on social media.
content:
